author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Init innovation in traffic systems buys back 1,741 shares at 21.10 EUR per share
text:
Sept 28 init innovation in traffic systems AG :
* In period between Sept. 21 and Sept. 25 bought back a total of 1,741 shares at an average price of 21.10 euros ($23.57) per share Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: ($1 = 0.8951 euros) (Gdynia Newsroom)
